**Rule 1**\nKeep things relevant to the channel you are participating in. It’s okay to be a bit off topic here and there, but it is important to realize and move to the proper channel to continue the conversation.
**Rule 2**\nKeep things civil. If there is a disagreement, stop when asked to stop.
**Rule 3**\nDo not be dismissive of others’ opinions.
**Rule 4**\nNo joking based on what people cannot immediately change. ie no jokes on race, weight, sexual orientation.
**Rule 5**\nAct your age, not your shoe size. Unless of course, your shoe size is somehow above your age, in such cases, act your shoe size.
**Rule 6**\nNo spamming the board.
**Rule 7**\nBe nice to everyone. Not following this rule will get you removed from the server quickly and effectively.
